
A simple calculator

Your calculator should provide the following arithmetic and control operations.

  Arithmetic Operations
      Addition (+)                  add(a,b)
      Subtraction (-)               subtract(a,b)
      Multiplication (*)            multiply(a,b)
      Division (/)                  divide(a,b)
      Power (^)                     power(a,b)
      Remainder (%)                 remainder(a,b)

  Control Operations
      Terminate (#)
      Reset ($)
